<xar:comment> 
Variables available in this template:
    match - the complete matched text
    template_base - the template base name
    template_name - the template main name
    error_text - the full error text
</xar:comment>
<xar:set name="$error_desc">xarML('Dynamic Autolink Error in template #(1)-#(2):', $template_base, $template_name)</xar:set>
<span class="xar-error" title="#$error_desc# #xarVarPrepForDisplay($error_text)#">#$match#</span>